OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a day of sunny
OL,6,Fspells and blustery showers, locally
OL,7,Fheavy, with the risk of hail and
OL,8,Fthunder in places. However, it should
OL,9,Ffeel quite pleasant in the sunshine,
OL,10,Fespecially in sheltered eastern parts,
OL,11,Fout of the wind.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny daytime showers will
OL,14,Fgradually ease to leave a dry night,
OL,15,Fwith prolonged clear spells. Winds
OL,16,Feasing, and turning locally chilly,
OL,17,Fwith a patchy frost forming in prone
OL,18,Frural spots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
