OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FAfter a bright and chilly
OL,6,Fstart, the clouds will begin to bubble
OL,7,Fup to give sunny spells and showers,
OL,8,Flocally heavy with hail and thunder,
OL,9,Finto the afternoon. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,12,Fwith sunny spells Tuesday, after
OL,13,Fanother chilly start. Cloud and
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain moving erratically
OL,15,Feast Wednesday, after early
OL,16,Fbrightness. Sunny spells and isolated
OL,17,Fshowers Thursday. Temperatures near
OL,18,Fnormal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
